column3: Cibleroit has a hunger for nanka eggs, and you must help him sate it. Harvest five eggs from a ninki nanka in the nearby river and bring them to him.
You have gathered the sticky, slimy nankaspawn. Get it off your hands as quickly as possible by delivering it to Cibleroit.

Cibleroit is delighted to receive the eggs. The Hungerer, however, thinks they are disgusting. Unlike the Gnath of the Onemind, differences of opinion─and all they entail─seem to be a unique characteristic of the Nonmind.
Slay a ninki nanka and obtain its eggs.
Generous hunter, we would like to ask something of you. It is not difficult work.
We need nanka eggs. Five delicious nanka eggs. <click> <click> Slay a ninki nanka and harvest its delicious eggs for us.
Do you have the eggs? Five succulent nanka eggs?
We wonder, will you never tire of nanka eggs, Cibleroit?
Do you have the nanka eggs? <click> <click> Tasty, juicy nanka eggs... <click> <click> <click>
<click> <click> Yesss. Thank you for these eggs. The texture is irresistible. We could eat a thousand of them...but five will do for now.
We cannot understand your liking for nanka eggs. They are disgusting. <click> <click> You have bad taste.
We cannot understand your dislike for nanka eggs. But this is what it means to be of the Nonmind.
